headline: Oura rings to track blood sugar, Vaccines vs RFK Jr., and Ozempic 2.0: Pharma news roundup
summary: Oura smart rings will soon be able to help users track their blood sugar levels through a new partnership with Dexcom (DXCM), the maker of the U.S.’s first over-the-counter continuous glucose monitor.
